#: ../../whatsnew/3.13.rst:2109
msgid ""
"Add the :c:func:`PyDict_GetItemRef` and :c:func:`PyDict_GetItemStringRef` "
"functions, which behave similarly to :c:func:`PyDict_GetItemWithError`, but "
