#: ../../whatsnew/3.13.rst:2283
msgid ""
"The *keywords* parameter of :c:func:`PyArg_ParseTupleAndKeywords` and :c:"
"func:`PyArg_VaParseTupleAndKeywords` now has type :c:expr:`char * const *` "
